    //   name (`grant_in[0]`, `grant_in[1]`, `grant_in[2]`) and each
    //   iteration emits ONE `connect_cond` row on `idx` carrying that
    //   wire as guard. pass_proc_mux (passes.hexa) then folds the 3
    //   cond-tagged rows into a left-deep `$mux` chain.
